>i run twm and would like to execut some program befor leav twm. in other
>word i would like to run some program befor i do f.quit. is it possibl
>to make a menu section which would contain these two part?

in your menu definit, put:

    "quit twm" f.function "execut and quit"

then defin:

function "execut and quit" {
    !"some_program"
    f.quit
}

